eckout: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.46.196:7070: i/o timeout\\\"\"\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"c993e6f9-65ae-4b79-8dba-e99d05404cde\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart/checkout\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"6c54187c-2827-4b4e-ad25-1766871b22a2\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-11T07:11:43.006351725Z\"\"}\",出现次数:23\naiops-k8s-01,checkoutservice,checkoutservice-1,\"{\"\"message\"\":\"\"failed to send order confirmation to \\\"\"someone@example.com\\\"\": rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"warning\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-11T07:15:29.654911871Z\"\"}\",出现次数:2\naiops-k8s-06,checkoutservice,checkoutservice-2,\"{\"\"message\"\":\"\"failed to send order confirmation to \\\"\"someone@example.com\\\"\": rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"warning\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-11T07:15:35.507757543Z\"\"}\",出现次数:2\naiops-k8s-04,frontend,frontend-2,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = cart failure: failed to get user cart during checkout: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.46.196:7070: i/o timeout\\\"\"\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"cff65225-b318-4717-a956-328584173848\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart/checkout\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"dbacfbb6-9be3-474e-8a62-795ec631829a\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-11T07:26:13.82915499Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["frontend-2", "frontend-1", "frontend-0", "checkoutservice-1", "checkoutservice-2"], "service_name": ["frontend", "checkoutservice"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-04", "aiops-k8s-07", "aiops-k8s-03", "aiops-k8s-01", "aiops-k8s-06"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault was detected from 2025-06-11T07:10:39Z to 2025-06-11T07:30:39Z. Please analyze its root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-11 07:10:39+00:00 to 2025-06-11 07:30:39+00:00"}, "log_data_collected": true, "trace_analysis_findings": "以下是从2025-06-11T07:10:39Z到2025-06-11T07:30:39Z期间检测到的故障的数据分析与发现：\n\n### 关键数据概览\n\n1. **延迟异常**：\n   - `hipstershop.CartService/GetCart`: 异常时段平均耗时显著增加，倍数达到了2744.8倍。\n   - `hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder`: 异常时段平均耗时增至154倍。\n\n2. **错误状态码**：\n   - `connection error` 和 `rpc error` 是最频繁的错误，出现在多个节点和服务之间。\n   - `timed out waiting for server handshake` 表示网络连接或下游服务无法响应。\n\n3. **调用异常**：\n   - `frontend-0`至`checkoutservice-2`以及`checkoutservice-1`多个调用的异常。\n   - `hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder` 和 `hipstershop.CartService/GetCart` 是异常集中的两个关键操作。\n\n### 异常指标分析\n\n- **高延迟（rrt_max）**：\n  - `hipstershop.CartService/GetCart`与`hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder`均出现显著于正常值的延迟。\n  \n- **错误传播路径**：\n  - 错误从`checkoutservice`开始，传播至其下游。\n  - `connection errors`和`rpc errors`提示有连接问题可能源自`checkoutservice`相关的pod。\n\n### 根因假设\n根据分析，根因很可能是由于`checkoutservice`内部或者其下游的服务出现了连接问题，导致`CartService/GetCart`和`CheckoutService/PlaceOrder`的正常操作无法完成。这可能是因网络故障或服务自身的负载过高造成的。\n\n### 输出格式 (JSON)\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->frontend\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"异常时段的耗时大幅增加，超过正常时段多倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"HTTP状态码500频率增加，影响接收功能\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"connection error及rpc error连接问题频繁出现\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n以上为当前分析得到的关键信息和可能的故障根因。如果需要更详细的系统性能数据，进一步的日志和指标采集可能是必要的。", "log_analysis_findings": "通过分析提供的日志数据，我提取了以下关键信息：\n\n### Detected Log Keys\n- **timeout**\n- **connection error**\n- **transport: Error while dialing**\n- **context canceled**\n\n### Hypotheses\n\n1. **Component**: frontend service\n   - **Reason**: Multiple instances of the frontend service encountered connection timeouts while attempting to communicate with backend services. This suggests issues with network latency or connectivity problems between services.\n   - **Evidence**: Multiple log entries indicating `\"error\": \"failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = cart failure: failed to get user cart during checkout: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error...\"`\n\n2. **Component**: checkoutservice\n   - **Reason**: There are warnings in the checkout service logs for order confirmation failures due to a `context canceled` error, indicating potential issues in processing requests or internal cancellations.\n   - **Evidence**: Log example: `\"message\": \"failed to send order confirmation to \\\"someone@example.com\\\": rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled\"`\n\n### Conclusion\nThe primary issue appears to be network-related, likely causing the frontend service to experience connectivity issues when communicating with backend services. Additionally, the checkout service also showed errors, potentially linking to broader system-wide issues or targeted backend stress.\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"timeout\", \"connection error\", \"transport: Error while dialing\", \"context canceled\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend service\",\n      \"reason\": \"Instances encountered connection timeouts while communicating with backend services.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Multiple log entries indicating \\\"connection error\\\"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Warnings for order confirmation failures due to 'context canceled' errors.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Log indicating \\\"context canceled\\\"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "metric_analysis_findings": "我们已经成功加载了故障期间的指标数据，现在进入初步扫描分析阶段。\n\n### 异常指标数据\n分析的目标是识别异常的调用链、资源瓶颈或性能问题。以下是故障期间检测到的一些关键异常指标：\n\n1. **Frontend Service**\n   - **Metrics**: `server_error_ratio`, `error_ratio`, `rrt`, `rrt_max`\n   - **Pods**: `frontend-0`, `frontend-1`, `frontend-2`\n   - **Observations**: 指标显示显著的响应时间和错误率增高。\n\n2. **Shipping Service**\n   - **Metrics**: `client_error_ratio`, `error_ratio`\n   - **Pods**: `shippingservice-1`, `shippingservice-2`\n   - **Observations**: 指标显示从正常到高错误率，尤其在 `shippingservice-2` 的客户端错误比率达到60%。\n\n3. **Cart Service**\n   - **Metrics**: `rrt`, `rrt_max`, `error_ratio`, `client_error_ratio`\n   - **Pods**: `cartservice-1`, `cartservice-2`\n   - **Observations**: 错误率跳跃，响应时间也有显著增长，尤其 `cartservice-1` 的最大响应时间显著增加。\n\n4. **Checkout Service**\n   - **Metrics**: `rrt`, `rrt_max`\n   - **Pods**: `checkoutservice-1`, `checkoutservice-2`\n   - **Observations**: 响应时间大幅增加，尤其 `checkoutservice-1`。\n\n### 异常实体\n以下实体的异常指标显著，可能需进一步关注：\n- Pods: `frontend-0`, `frontend-1`, `frontend-2`, `shippingservice-1`, `shippingservice-2`, `cartservice-1`, `cartservice-2`, `checkoutservice-1`, `checkoutservice-2`\n\n### JSON 输出格式\n基于初步分析，构建以下JSON输出：\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"client_error_ratio\", \"error_ratio\", \"rrt\", \"rrt_max\", \"server_error_ratio\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Elevated server_error_ratio and error_ratio with increased rrt and rrt_max values indicates potential service logic issues or resource constraints.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"fault_median server_error_ratio 0.3, fault_p99 rrt_max 242744.6\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"Client error ratio spikes to 60% indicating possible upstream failures or resource bottleneck.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"fault_p99 client_error_ratio 60.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant increase in rrt_max and error_ratio highlights a potential scalability or resource management issue.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"fault_p99 rrt_max 22501013.11, fault_median error_ratio 0.0\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n若需进一步详细的分析或补充其他信息，请告知。接下来可以进行深入的指标相关性分析。"}
